{"tid":2197042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國外交部國務部長: 明白美國憂慮 但妖魔化中國會危害國際局勢穩定 德國無意脫鉤/限制中國","createTime":"2020-09-10T10:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T20:32:38.000Z","uid":270889,"like":20,"dislike":227,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0429e5e8b9234f4ec50861e5e6b010373a487c","tid":2197042,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:24:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/noahbarkin/status/1303742162316734465?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnoahbarkin%2Fstatus%2F1303742162316734465%3Fs%3D20&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=1032238d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnoahbarkin%2Fstatus%2F1303742162316734465%3Fs%3D20&h=276c3d08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/noahbarkin/status/1303742162316734465?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n睇comment外國人(好似包括德國人)都一定倒圍插佢 <br />\n大家再補多兩句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">精選comments:</span><br />\n<em>Germany wants to make money, whatever it takes. Even the price is silencing on crimes against humanity in CCP-China. Annen, former leader of the far-left youth organization of the <br />\nSocial Democrats, boasts anti-Americanism, instead of promoting universal human and civil rights.<br />\n<br />\nCountry that once ran concentration camps doesn't want to decouple from or contain another country that runs present-day concentration camps because money.<br />\n<br />\nThey are repeating their own ancestral mistakes. Germany went through a lot of hardship to let the world know that they have past through the holocaust incident &amp; now the new Germany is bringing it all back. It's like business as usual with hitler himself.<br />\n<br />\nKeine Konsequenzen f&uuml;r KZs, und das aus Deutschland. Besch&auml;mend. Ihr h&auml;ttet Euch in dem 1930er auch weggeduckt<br />\n<ins>No consequences for concentration camps, and that from Germany. Shameful. You would have ducked away in the 1930s</ins> (google translate)<br />\n<br />\nEr hat sicherlich die Vernichtung der Juden vergessen, ansonsten werde er nicht wegsehen, was in Xingjiang zu den Uyghuren passiert ist.<br />\n<ins>He has certainly forgotten the extermination of the Jews, otherwise he will not look the other way about what happened to the Uyghurs in Xingjiang.</ins> (google translate)<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Neither decopuling or containment&quot;<br />\nThen what? More &quot;change through trade&quot; BS?</em>"},{"pid":"418d722c6e216b731dda255d5e49a6b2c8f3bcec","tid":2197042,"uid":19126,"like":71,"dislike":3,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"德國狗政府不如直接話自己加入中共，負責接管歐洲好過啦，反正都做慣邪惡軸心國啦"},{"pid":"01c3a2479d1598be57f57d3876314d27a85bdf9e","tid":2197042,"uid":270889,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:30:24.000Z","msg":"條友2019年訪問上海 話有重點談及新疆問題<br />\n但係官網篇文.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n德国外交部国务部长安恩日前访问北京和上海，就贸易政策、军控和气候变化进行会谈，<span class=\"red\">因为所有全球大挑战都绕不开中国</span>。<br />\n今非昔比，现已成为世界第二大经济体的中国在国际上的影响力越来越大，伊朗问题、军控、气候变化等全球大挑战若<span class=\"red\">无中国参与，难以取得进展</span>。而且<span class=\"red\">中国身为出口大国，也很重视基于规则的、可靠的世界贸易制度。中国和欧洲积极交流，共同寻找解决当前贸易冲突的出路</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.diplo.de/cn-zh/vertretungen/gk-shanghai/20190716/2234926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.diplo.de%2Fcn-zh%2Fvertretungen%2Fgk-shanghai%2F20190716%2F2234926&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=64d34ad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.diplo.de/cn-zh/vertretungen/gk-shanghai/20190716/2234926</a>"},{"pid":"79aa86748d834335c3b3c1a1566279f2bc8c269d","tid":2197042,"uid":47492,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T10:30:56.000Z","msg":"你老母 咁都叫妖魔化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   根本係魔鬼"},{"pid